Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.04,0:00:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[kids playing and shouting]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[child crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-[child crying loudly]\N-[rattling]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-[child continues crying]\N-[rattling continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[child screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[bell tolls]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[bell tolls]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[bell tolls]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[bell tolls]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[bell tolls]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[rattling and crackling]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,SILENCE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A corner of a page of this notebook\Nhas been torn off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you kill someone\Njust by writing their name on a piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never tried using it like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't know of anyone who has.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let me ask you,\Ndo Gods of Death love apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, our internal organs\Nhave already degraded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We've evolved
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to a point where we\Ndo not require sustenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[smacks] Say, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finally free to leave headquarters\Non your own,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but it seems like you never go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when Misa comes to visit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you only chat with her\Nfor a few minutes outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You do realize you're free\Nto have a relationship with her now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That can wait\Nuntil we've managed to solve this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in the mood\Nfor love or anything else right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:04:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, are you suggesting\Nthat I'll be a nuisance for staying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[suspenseful choral music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Right now, I'm in no position\Nto continue punishing criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I need you\Nto punish them for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,let's create a new world together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[kids playing outside]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[chiming]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,WANTED - SHINJUKU, TOKYO\NSHINTAROMARU MARUYAMADA (43)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[singing] Careful what you do…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause God is watching your every move
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold my hand in the dark street
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,For if you do, I know that I'll be safe
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm far away and alone
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can be sure that you'll find me there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This I know
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You draw me close for a while, so quiet
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You tell me everything
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If I forget what you say
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'd come to me and tell me again
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you'd tell me once again
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But what happens when I know it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what should I do after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard criminals are being killed again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] There were 16 death\Njust yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them were broadcast\Nafter Higuchi's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Immediately after, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think this could mean
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that Higuchi wasn't necessarily Kira\Nafter all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's safe to say that Higuchi\Nwas the one killing criminals
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,until we apprehended him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this means we're dealing\Nwith yet another Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, man! Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. Damn you, Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Another Kira's appeared.\NWhat's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:07:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,These killings began\Nas soon as Misa was freed, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, are you still going on\Nabout that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She has nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it.\NThis started as soon as Higuchi died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I suppose you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well... If there is another notebook\Nfloating around out there
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and someone is now using it\Nto kill criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to bring that person\Nto justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[smacks]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shinigami insisted\Nthat it didn't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but if someone were able to kill
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,simply by writing a name\Non a torn piece of the notebook…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but there is that rule,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"Whoever writes a name in this notebook\Nhas to write another name within 13 days,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise they die."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami and Misa Amane\Nare both still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirteen days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Ryuzaki, I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we do manage to catch the person\Nwho’s been writing names in the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,will we really be able to legally\Nconvict and punish them for mass homicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Of course, we can convict them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy’s intentionally\Nwriting names in the notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing that these people\Nare going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we don't plan\Non publicly acknowledging the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the least we can do is execute the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] It's not a very humane way\Nto do things,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but the higher-ups would\Nprobably wanna take measures like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If they admit\Nto killing with the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,they'd receive the death penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Or a life in prison at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[muffled] That’s the best\Nthat they could hope for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking, Light Yagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Making Misa kill again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be caught and once that happens,\Nyou'll also be--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what your plan is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're truly disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami is certain
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that I will do anything\Nto help Misa and save her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And at this point,\Nthe only way for me to save Misa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:09:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is to write Ryuzaki's real name\Nin my notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I kill Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It would mean that I deliberately\Nlengthened Misa's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and I will die as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami has planned everything,\Nso that it will work out in his favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do, Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be a Shinigami,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can't hide the fact\Nthat you care for Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way\Nyou would turn your back on her now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,after she's already\Nhalved her lifespan twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Think about Misa's happiness…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[eerie ambient noise]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing standing out there\Nby yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing standing out there\Nby yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not doing anything in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear the bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of the bell's\Nbeen unusually loud today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Really? You can't hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been ringing non-stop all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I find it... very distracting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's a church...\Nmaybe a wedding, or perhaps a...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you getting at, Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, cut it out.\NLet's get back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing I say makes any sense anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] If I were you,\NI wouldn't believe any of it…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you're totally right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, most of the things you say\Nsound like complete nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There'd be no end to my troubles
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,if I actually took you seriously\Nall the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably know that better than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say that's a fair assessment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I could say the same about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Light,\Nfrom the moment you were born,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,has there ever been a point\Nwhen you've actually told the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this coming from, Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I do admit, I stretch the truth\Nhere and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,However, find me one person in this world\Nwho's never had to tell a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Human beings just aren't made\Nto be perfect like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody lies from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always made a conscious effort\Nto be careful
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,not to tell a lie\Nthat could hurt others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a feeling you'd say\Nsomething like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're both drenched.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[water dripping]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Well, that was certainly\Nan unpleasant outing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your own fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what did you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I might help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You were busy wiping yourself off anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Look, it's fine.\NYou don't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can give you a massage as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the least I can do\Nto atone for my sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually pretty good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] You'll get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. You're still soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-[L] It'll be lonely, won't it?\N-[Light] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I will be parting ways soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's go, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like it's all worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Ryuzaki,\Nwhat's the meaning of all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You've somehow\Ngot an approval from another country
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to use the notebook for an execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Watari, excellent work. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] First things first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, make arrangements\Nto transport the notebook immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, what are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:16:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] I'm gonna try out the notebook\Nfor real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[all gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's no point\Nin testing it now
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,when we already know\Nthe notebook's power is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] And besides,\Nwho's gonna write the name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone starts writing in the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,they will have to obey the 13-day rule\Nand keep writing names forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] It's already been worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who will write in the notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is a criminal scheduled to be executed\Nin just over 13 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's still alive\N13 days after writing the name,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-he will be pardoned from execution.\N-[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-But still, to sacrifice a life--\N-[L] We're very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If we work this out,\Nthe entire case will be solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-[alarm blaring]\N-[Matsuda] What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Watari?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Watari!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Data deletion?\NWhat the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Watari to make sure\Nthat he should erase all information
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in the event that something\Nwere to happen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If something were to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Good question. I don't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, the Shiniga--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[loud heartbeat]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:18:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ryuzaki! What's wrong?\N-[bell tolls]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[bell tolls]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[bell continues tolling]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Hey! Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-What happened?\N-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.02,0:19:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Watari, Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be us next!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Shinigami? Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know something about this, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] We better go and look too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogi, take over for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Sand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Whatever it might mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever happens next...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, I will avenge Ryuzaki's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to solve this case
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,in honor of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and for Watari...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the other victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this. For them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.86,0:20:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't we all gonna get killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what all of this really means?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuda, if you're afraid of dying,\Nthen leave the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We put our lives on the line\Nwhen we chose to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But... It-- It's weird\Nhearing you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:20:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound like Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[door closes]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotten rid of everything in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[dramatic music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[lightning crashes]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the god of the new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme song plays]